		{ ref: `Isaiah 46:4`, slug: `isaiah`, ch: 46, text: `Even to your old age and gray hairs I am He who will sustain you. I have made you and I will carry you; I will sustain you and I will rescue you.`, note: `The same Father who carries the one you're caring for promises to carry you, all the way to the end.` },
