	offersHeading={`What "our Father" offers you`}
	offersIntroHtml={`Caregiving asks you to keep giving when you're empty. Here's what your Father gives you instead — for free, because you're already His.`}
	offersBlocks={[
		{ heading: `Rest for the weary`, bodyHtml: `When you're running on no sleep and no margin, hear it: <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/matthew/11" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">come to Me, all you who are weary, and I will give you rest</a>. Your Father's first invitation to the exhausted caregiver is simply to come.` },
		{ heading: `Strength when your tank is empty`, bodyHtml: `When you've got nothing left, <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/isaiah/40" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">those who hope in your Father renew their strength</a> — they walk and don't faint. His power picks up exactly where yours runs out.` },
		{ heading: `A Father who carries your burden daily`, bodyHtml: `You are not carrying this alone. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/psalms/68" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Your Father daily bears your burdens</a> — every appointment, every fear, every long night. He shoulders the weight right alongside you.` },
		{ heading: `The promise that He carries you too`, bodyHtml: `The same God who holds the one you love also holds you: <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/isaiah/46" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">I have made you and I will carry you</a>. To your old age and gray hairs, your Father will sustain you.` },
	]}
	whyHeading={`Why the Father's Heart Bible™ for caregivers`}
	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet God as a Father, not a taskmaster`, bodyHtml: `Many Bibles can read like one more set of demands — one more person needing something from you. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as a <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> on. So instead of one more voice asking you to give, you meet the One who wants to fill you back up.` },
		{ heading: `It's free, on your phone, with audio`, bodyHtml: `No account, no purchase, no app. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — listen in the hospital waiting room, in the car between appointments, or with your eyes closed at 3 a.m. when sleep won't come. The Father's voice fits into the cracks of your caregiving day.` },
		{ heading: `It speaks to what you're actually facing`, bodyHtml: `Burned out? Grieving someone who's still here? Wondering who you are anymore? Start with our <a href="/verses/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">verses by topic</a> or learn to talk to Him with our <a href="/guides/how-to-pray/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">how-to-pray guide</a> — the Word meets you right where you are.` },
